X:259
T:The Lord's My Shepherd
C:Words: Psalm 23 from the Scottish Psalter, 1650 alt. by James Leith Macbeth Bain, 1915.
C:Music: 'Marosa' or 'Brother James' Air', James Leith Macbeth Bain, 1915.
C:SSAATTBB arrangement expanded from Open Hymnal Project SATB source.
C:Copyright: public domain.
M:3/2
L:1/4
Q:1/2=70
%%staves [(1 2) (3 4) (5 6) (7 8)]
